  "outcome": "Continuation higher confirmed with two days of expansion following the failed reversal at the FVG.",
  "lessons": "When price reaches a point of interest without producing an aggressive reversal reaction, treat it as a continuation signal rather than forcing a counter-trend trade; let the next candle confirm the new phase.",
